 in the 1990s]]\n[[Category:Films set in the 2000s]]\n[[Category:Films set in the 2010s]]\n[[Category:Films set in Maryland]]\n[[Category:Films set in the White House]]\n[[Category:Films set in Virginia]]\n[[Category:Films set in Washington, D.C.]]\n[[Category:Films set in Wyoming]]\n[[Category:Films that won the Academy Award for Best Makeup]]\n[[Category:Gary Sanchez Productions films]]\n[[Category:Plan B Entertainment films]]\n", "name_user": "Trappist the monk", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eCritical response:remove 'invisible' characters from cs1|2 template parameters; (2\u00d7 NBSP)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vice_(2018_film)"}
